{"tid":153794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「連登仔」徒步由東京行到京都　網民大讚有毅力","createTime":"2017-03-12T19:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T07:39:44.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cb464f0fc7808b051cb0b535feb786e339768d0","tid":153794,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T19:56:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/0/20170309/547814/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F0%2F20170309%2F547814%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3Mn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=9fd9d144\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Fcolumns%2F0%2F20170309%2F547814%2F&h=d729163f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/columns/0/20170309/547814/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/03/09/74306/i_640x1023_048701972.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F74306%2Fi_640x1023_048701972.jpg&h=d2153b5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">要由東京行到京都一啲都唔易。</span><br />\n<br />\n最新網絡討論區叫「連登」，雖然啱啱開始獨立運作，但入面就有兩個連登仔做緊一個創舉，就喺兩條友徒步由東京行到京都！<br />\n<br />\n　　呢兩個網民，喺「連登」發表佢哋嘅計劃同直擊每日行程，引嚟大批連登仔熱烈討論。呢個徒步之旅由自稱Moyashi嘅網民發起，之後佢個朋友加入一齊出發，佢哋喺今個月四號宣佈，準備沿東海道由東京行到京都。<br />\n<br />\n　　佢哋亦唔係得個講字，即刻就去Google map搵到，如果不眠不休咁行，四、五日就可以去到目的地。最後佢哋決定用十六日去行，第一日喺由日本橋行到浜松駅，接近三十公里嘅路程，預計行六個鐘。睇翻佢哋嘅直擊報道，佢哋最後行咗九個幾鐘，行到腰痛、腳痛，仲生水泡O添！<br />\n<br />\n　　網民見到佢哋咁有毅力，都留言讚佢哋好勁，有喺日本嘅連登仔仲話想請佢哋食飯，Kelly都好佩服佢哋啊！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2017/03/09/74306/i_640x665_041869865.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2017%2F03%2F09%2F74306%2Fi_640x665_041869865.jpg&h=b435a1b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">睇地圖已經知道要完成呢個創舉一啲都唔易。</span><br />\nKelly Chu"},{"pid":"16275c9c47d8072e419a3ee2a66671431b620cb2","tid":153794,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T20:03:22.000Z","msg":"冇睇過"},{"pid":"8352fac26357131c0e1c2cfb1ab81e5576cedc20","tid":153794,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdbfbbb8f9edd04086967e7a3d04f9391e6c0671","tid":153794,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:24:38.000Z","msg":"行路撚走火入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb074b560b35e812d0500129fa7f87100775baf","tid":153794,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T21:25:02.000Z","msg":"又係你呀浜松"},{"pid":"e92ecc8f514074106f89000ba8914c09ec83a671","tid":153794,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"邊撚過kelly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己寫文引自己個名真係好on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a2bdaf5d333f4b450f574af22cb860c25c3abb","tid":153794,"uid":56702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:37:43.000Z","msg":"乜水呀kelly<br />\n以為打機果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e758404fdc7d51f8a072de27e84263e032bd40c4","tid":153794,"uid":70538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜水呀kelly<br />\n以為打機果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n罵自己個個"},{"pid":"681e5280d785b05647027649c7c0e066457316e9","tid":153794,"uid":89309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T00:44: